Purchased their bundle set for reunion lunch, consisting of braised duck, roasted chicken and braised meat. The braised duck was dry and hard. Roasted chicken and braised meat were dry. Thought of having the leftovers (without sauce) for a meal the next day but all had a sour smell. The meat (not even warm) was all in a bag when I arrived to collect. My first and last time purchasing from them. Cost me $75. Do reconsider before you place an order.

Everything including the soup was of terrible standard. Instead of the signature herbal taste, it's only msg and nothing else. So-called "yam" rice just ordinary rice in soya sauce. The meat was tough and tasteless. Totally cannot make it.

Okay tasty food. Reasonable portion for the price. Service is fast and helpful.

Stall located at Level 1 of Jurong Hawker Center.

Pls maintain the standard for the Brand.
